item.title: About
item.dc:creator: nathanziemanski
item.content:encoded:
VolleySmash is an annual beach volleyball tournament and league put on by former and current volleyball players in BC. The tournament takes place on Spanish Banks Beach located in Vancouver. The tournament and league entry fee is by donation and all proceeds go toward funding kids sport who cannot afford it. Over the last 5 years, VolleySmash has grown from a total of 6 teams to well over 80 teams. This website will help spread the word about the tournament in hope of growing the number of participants even more.
